% Prepreamble follows.
<<LaTeXPrePreamble>>

% Load the documentclass.
\documentclass[%
journal = <<TemplateBaseName>>,
manuscript = article,
layout = twocolumn,
<<DocumentClassOptions>>]{achemso}

% Turn on section numbering.
\SectionNumbersOn

% Preamble follows.
<<LaTeXPreamble>>

% Setup document metadata.
\makeatletter
\@ifpackageloaded{hyperref}{%
	\hypersetup{
		pdftitle = {<<Title>>},
		pdfauthor = {<<AuthorsFullNamesCommaSeparated>>},
		pdfkeywords = {<<KeywordsCommaSeparated>>},
		pdfcreator = {<<ScoopTemplateEngineSignature>>}
	}
}{
	\pdfinfo{
		/Title (<<Title>>)
